node.text: Knowing & understanding your work never be easy to do and to hold on,
But, your words really make me to think, to be positive, so don't give up, stay safe stay strong, you can do it! 👍👏

I long for the empty streets and miles to go before I sleep. For the untamed freedom of stories untold. 😍👍🏻
.
For long dark nights not a soul in sight. For the throbbing heartbeat of the open road! ♥️👍🏻
.
It has been a journey battling with everyone in this world with the coronavirus. And this is gonna be a long waiting game. I truly felt staying away from your love ones is an act of responsibility. It's something I can comprehend but still hard to accept. ♥️👍🏻
.
Even tho it is hard not able to travel, but I still count my blessings, at least I can still do my part. At least I can comfortably stay at home! 🥰👍🏻
.
To be honest, I delighted to hear many encouraging words that there are people looking forward to my positive message everyday. I honestly didnt even believe there will be people interested in my thoughts, in my words and my sharings. 🙏🏻
.
There are times I thought about giving up postings and all social media stuff... but I realised I actually established many real connections with amazing people like you. That also provides me positivity and words of encouragement. Sharing with me your stories and reminding me know I'm blessed. ♥️👍🏻
.
I guess this is the blessings I have for all the "hard work" through these years om Travel Inspiration 360. My tagline... "to inspire and be inspired". Indeed, what goes around comes around. 😍👍🏻
.
Pls all stay safe, we are in this together! No differences in race, gender, social status, religion, or looks. It's all about doing our part to save our lives again! Let's continue to keep a positive mind and stay at home! ♥️🙏🏻
.
Sending loves from 🇸🇬
.
